      <div class="model-card"><h3>Column-integrated ice</h3><p>Sub-Zero-style column integration on luxury LG Signature + SKS platform (see <a href="/brands/signature-kitchen-suite-ice-maker-repair/">SKS</a> if luxury-tier).</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LT800P water filter + replacement cycle</h3><p>Standard LG refrigerator water filter. 6-month replacement schedule. Filter drives ice-fill pressure.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Residential LG ice maker vs commercial ice machines</h2>
    <p>LG is residential-only — LG doesn't sell commercial ice machines. Residential LG ice makers produce 3-8 lb/day typical across InstaView + French-door + side-by-side formats. For restaurant, bar, or commercial hospitality ice production at 200+ lb/day scale, you need commercial ice equipment (Manitowoc, Hoshizaki, Scotsman, Follett) — completely different refrigeration architecture, separate service scope, health-department-coded. See <a href="/commercial/ice-machine-repair/">commercial ice machine repair</a> for production-scale intent. This page covers residential LG refrigerator-integrated ice making only.</p>
